reviewText: the movie is action packed and silly .......she has no emotions and is like the terminator only a women ...great scenery ,lots of bullets missing the marks ....and very cheesy scene with a whole army of more than 80 men being killed, by 2 guys in a truck cashing a road block well worth the price of the DVD.
Wow, this is a sequel to a remake of a French film. This movie has nice action, but the acting and plotting are more or less typical. An  entertaining rental if you can find it.
